            "detailed_description": "<h1>Content Patch!</h1><p><strong>PATCH HISTORY:</strong><br><br>- <strong>1.2</strong> - 05/01/2018 at 4:00PM EST<br>Major bug fixes, thanks everyone for your contribution and support!<br><br>- <strong>1.1.2</strong> - 2/14/2018 at 8:05PM EST<br>Added: Further optimization. Fixed: Tutorial bug (failing when shooting and hitting nothing [sky])<br><br>- <strong>1.1</strong> - 2/11/2018 at 9:50PM EST<br>Added auto-pause / unpause based on HMD Worn state, fixed a few mission bugs and optimized the game further.<br><br>- <strong>1.0.9</strong> - 2/5/2018 at 4:30AM EST<br><strong>Arcade Mode #3 Added!</strong> + Fixed: A few bugs.<br><br>- <strong>1.0.8</strong> - 2/3/2018 at 10:39PM EST<br><strong>Arcade Mode #2 Added!</strong> + A Holographic sight to non-sniping, fast-paced missions. Fixed: A few mission bugs.<br><br>- <strong>1.0.7</strong> - 1/31/2018 at 9:06PM EST<br><strong>Steam Achievements Added!</strong> + Bug Patch. Fixed the HTC Vive controller rotations, they now feel natural.<br><br>- <strong>1.0.6</strong> - 1/30/2018 at 1:26PM EST<br><strong>Arcade Mode #1 Added!</strong> + Bug Patch. Fixed a few fade-in/out bugs and the player's height during transitional environments. <br><br>- <strong>1.0.5</strong> - 1/28/2018 at 10:28PM EST<br><strong>Visual enhancement patch!</strong> Also now preventing players from clipping through vehicle(s).<br><br>- <strong>1.0.4</strong> - 1/27/2018 at 11:48AM EST<br>Fixed the audio bug on HTC Vive and a few HMD issues towards end-game.<br><br>- <strong>1.0.3</strong> - 1/26/2018 at 2:39AM EST<br>Optimization and a few bug fixes.<br><br>- <strong>1.0.2</strong> - 1/25/2018 at 11:37PM EST<br>Bug Patch. The reload 'eject shell' mechanic fixed on a few missions.<br><br>- <strong>1.0.1</strong> - 1/25/2018 at 9:37PM EST<br>Bug Patch. Arcade button fixed along with a few mission bugs.<br><br>- <strong>1.0.0</strong> - 1/22/2018 at 8:00AM EST<br><strong>Full Content Unlock! </strong>The storyline is now available.<br><br>If you encounter any bugs, please use the form via the link below to contact us directly.<br>We work hard to resolve problems with our games and we'll get right on it!<br><br><strong>Bug Report:</strong> <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://form.jotform.com/80247442929260\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >https://form.jotform.com/80247442929260</a></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>The <i>Romano</i> family has taken over the city. Corrupt politicians and police agencies do nothing to stop them. Become the morally ambiguous champion this city needs as a <strong>Sniper in Virtual Reality</strong>.<br><br><strong>The Perfect Sniper</strong> is a stylized, story-driven and action-packed VR game that lets you take on the role of a deadly vigilante as you take down the <i>Romanos</i>, an organized crime family involved in an underground market for weapons, drugs and human trafficking. Tactical target eliminations, car chases and more; prevent minor crime with sharp precision and stop major crime with nothing but deadly force. <br><br><img src=\"https://%CDN_HOST_MEDIA_SSL%/steam/apps/749370/extras/InDesc2.jpg?t=1532605422\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"><br><br><strong>FEATURES:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An Epic Storyline<br></li><li>Lots of Sniper Action<br></li><li>Target Elimination Missions<br></li><li>Car Chases<br></li><li>Helicopters<br></li><li>Cinematic Sequences<br></li><li>Lots of Fan Request Implementation<br></li><li>Beautiful Summer and Winter Maps</li></ul><br>Embark on a deadly mission and become the Perfect Sniper. Take down a massive underground criminal organization as a one-man army.<br>The Romanos' won't see you coming; the cavalry is here.",
